data.title: Walla Walla Union Bulletin
data.meta_description: This is a {category name} for {deceased name} published on {publish date} in {publication name}
data.text:
Dennis LeFore

Dennis 'Randy' LeFore of Milton-Freewater passed away on August 21, 2024 at the age of 70 years. He was born on January 14, 1954. Munselle-Rhodes Funeral Home, 902 S. Main, Milton-Freewater is in charge of the arrangements.

Marvin Dahl

Marvin L. Dahl of Milton-Freewater and formerly of Walla Walla passed away on August 19, 2024 at the age of 90 years. He was born on February 19, 1934. Services are pending. Munselle-Rhodes Funeral Home, 902 S. Main, Milton-Freewater is in charge of the arrangements.

Keith Reardon

Walla Walla resident Keith Reardon, 65, died August 9, 2024, at Providence St. Mary Medical Center.

A full obituary and guestbook will soon be available at https://www.herringgroseclose.com.

Norma Baisch

Walla Walla resident Norma Amelia Baisch, 95, died July 17, 2024, at her home.

A full obituary and guestbook are available at https://www.herringgroseclose.com

Donald Records

Donald 'Don' Records of Walla Walla and formerly of Umapine passed away on July 21, 2024 in Walla Walla at the age of 92 years. He was born on September 4, 1931. Munselle-Rhodes Funeral Home, Milton-Freewater is in charge of the arrangements. Please visit: www.munsellerhodes.com for further service details.

Shirley Allen

Walla Walla resident Shirley L. Allen, 96, died July 19, 2024. A full obituary and guestbook are available at mountainview-colonialdewitt.com.

Leon Bannister

Walla Walla resident Leon Burnett Bannister, 94, died July 17, 2024. A full obituary and guestbook are available at mountainview-colonialdewitt.com.

Frederic Hair II

Frederic William Hair II, 90, died July 11, 2024, at his home in College Place.

Arrangements are pending at Herring Groseclose Funeral Home, 315 W Alder St, Walla Walla.

John Severin

Walla Walla resident John Patrick "Pat" Severin, 81, died May 25, 2024. A full obituary and guestbook are available at mountainview-colonialdewitt.com.

Frank Lepiane

Frank Ross Lepiane, 91, died July 14, 2024, at Providence St. Mary Medical Center.

Graveside service on July 18, 2024, at 10am at Mountain View Cemetery, followed by a memorial service at 11am, at the Chapel of the Herring Funeral Home with Chaplain Lloyd Perrin officiating.

Doris Chryst

Doris Bessie Chryst of Pendleton, was born in Milton, Oregon on November 18, 1927 to John K. Phillips and Jessie Opal Noyes. She passed away July 3rd, 2024 at her son's home in Walla Walla, WA.

John Witwer

Celebration of Life for Johnny will be held at the Veteran's Memorial Golf Course, July 13th from 2-4pm.

Luella Dysart

Luella Nadine Dysart, 102, died July 3, 2024, at Providence St. Mary Medical Center.

A memorial service will be held on Thursday, July 25, 2024, at 2:00 PM, at Stateline Community Church, 85440 OR-11, Milton Freewater OR.

Gerald Keatts

Gerald Paul Keatts, 65, of Walla Walla, passed away on June 5, 2024. Services were held on June 15, 2024 at Herring Groseclose Funeral Home. Interment to be determined at a later date.

Ronald Ackerman

Ronald 'Ron' Ackerman of Milton-Freewater passed away on June 18, 2024 at his home at the age of 83 years. He was born on April 9, 1941.
